{"tid":1405684,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民文宣組］反攻家庭WhatsApp group,由你我做起","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T18:37:19.000Z","uid":200895,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"36ab867b10b99b2ef899043d12d0e9024f23aebe","tid":1405684,"uid":200895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:48:36.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人知道其實好多老一輩接收資料都不外乎Facebook, WhatsApp . <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook已經有巴打做緊，但要吸納大量藍絲、長輩非常困難，好難短時間內<span style=\"color: red;\">同化</span>藍絲。而且多數深藍已經知道邊啲係fake page<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而WhatsApp 家庭group 就易做好多，只要keep住放文宣資料班三姑六婆定會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加上依照以前佢地既習慣，佢哋睇完重會share出去其他WhatsApp group <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以各位只要不斷send 克警片 同 反送中資源， 有朝一日，<span style=\"color: red;\">WhatsApp 長辈家政group 一定會遍地開花</span></span>"},{"pid":"d28598540463e02d0620e4dde7b2696d912d35ad","tid":1405684,"uid":200895,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"文宣圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itjpgZL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitjpgZL.png&h=e6d70f64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sFcqS6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sFcqS6.png&h=1e5a2288&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pzP8JEM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpzP8JEM.png&h=4330e369&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfJ9s6s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgfJ9s6s.png&h=84dca714&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tGV76t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tGV76t.png&h=4f59f97d&s={SIZE}\" /><i